{"tid":2033030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方車隊離開天樂里時遭掟磚　一名警員受傷流血","createTime":"2020-05-24T11:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T11:45:26.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe10c3247d4178931d30f84b2d8380cfaf09b7e","tid":2033030,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/202005/100716125_3203521779735764_6430194073704857600_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F202005%2F100716125_3203521779735764_6430194073704857600_n.jpg&h=3d210843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方表示，今日（5月24日）傍晚接近6時，在銅鑼灣鵝頸橋完成執法後離開，當警方的車隊駛至天樂里時，有「暴徒」向警車投擲磚頭。其中一輛警察私家車車頭司機位整塊玻璃窗被擊碎，大量玻璃碎片濺進車廂，一名警員受傷流血。<br />\n<br />\n警方又指，在較早前，亦有數名警務人員及市民遇襲受傷，需送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.passiontimes.hk/article/05-24-2020/62949\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F05-24-2020%2F62949&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMt5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=949d1954\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.passiontimes.hk/article/05-24-2020/62949</a>"},{"pid":"3f04d31fcfb45717cf24a7af9f1dccc106306802","tid":2033030,"uid":288765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:45:26.000Z","msg":"天滅奶共黑警"}]}